                h1 Have an idea you want to bounce off someone? What do you need help with?
                a.f2-m.f4.normal.link.near-black.b.ba.pv2.ph4.br2.center.pointer.hover(href="mailto:levi@curiosityio.com") Email me
                .center.pt3
